Class ApplicationProtocolNames

java.lang.Object
io.netty.handler.ssl.ApplicationProtocolNames
public final class ApplicationProtocolNames extends Object
Provides a set of protocol names used in ALPN and NPN.
See Also:
  • RFC7540 (HTTP/2)
  • RFC7301 (TLS ALPN Extension)
  • TLS NPN Extension Draft
